song_name: Its Time To Dance Cause Boys Will Be Boys

version_description: First version I've seen on here as it was only released 30 minutes before I started writing this. I'm not too sure about the Am to A switch, I can hear both in different places but I guess it's up to you to decide until we see them play live, then I will change it to the correct chord. Also the occasional F chord isn't certain either, just seems in the right place to me?
The final chorus is 1 step up, I have changed the chords there however you could just play the same chords but shift the capo to fret 3.

version_description: The strumming in the verses should be two quick strums per chord. When you get into the first pre-chorus you should strum the Em once, and the Dm and F as you hear it fit. There are tabs, that in the chorus have a C instead of a G (so feel free to use a C if you think it is more correct.).
